  "type": "mcq",
  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A rectangle has a length of <math alttext=\"3\"><mn>3</mn>\n</math> units and a width of <math alttext=\"39\"><mn>39</mn>\n</math> units. Which expression gives the area, in square units, of this rectangle?</p>",
