      "content": "<p><math alttext=\"2 left parenthesis 3 plus 39 right parenthesis\"><mn>2</mn><mfenced><mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow><mn>39</mn></mrow></mrow></mfenced></math></p>"
